<div class="preface">
    <h1>Highlights</h1>
    <p>
        <ol>
            <li>Define the validator by implementing <code>AsyncValidator</code>.</li>
            <li>
                The validator is debounced with
                <a href="https://www.learnrxjs.io/learn-rxjs/operators/utility/delay"><code>delay</code></a>
                to avoid doing too many HTTP requests.
            </li>
            <li>Set the custom validators with <code>FormBuilder</code>.</li>
            <li>Access the validation errors through the field getter.</li>
            <li>Access the state of the validation through <code>ngModel.pending</code></li>
        </ol>
    </p>
</div>

